title: Clancy Brothers - 1973 - Live on St. Patrick's Day (with Lou Kil
description:
A rare live album of Irish folk music performed by the Clancy Brothers and Louis Killen. "Live on St. Patrick's Day" has never been released on CD or mp3.


Live on St. Patrick's Day
1973-Audio Fidelity AFSD-6256 LP [with soloist]

1. The Barnyards of Delgaty [Tom Clancy]
2. Isn't It Grand Boys [Liam Clancy - Paddy Clancy - Louis Killen - Tom]
3. Finnegan's Wake [Liam]
4. Reilly's Daughter [Liam - Tom - Paddy - Lou - Liam]
5. Will You Go, Lassie [Liam]
6. The Patriot Game [Liam]
7. The Rising of the Moon [Tom]
8. Johnson's Motor Car [Liam - Paddy - Tom - Lou]

9. Brennan on the Moor [Paddy - Tom]
10. Carrickfergus [Tom]
11. Nancy Whiskey [Lou - Paddy - Tom - Liam]
12. Monday Morning [Lou]
13. The Wild Colonial Boy [Liam - Paddy - Tom]
14. I'll Tell Me Ma When I Go Home [Liam (brief)]
15. The Wild Rover [Liam]
16. Parting Glass [Liam]
